Asymptomatic Patients With Brugada ECG Pattern: Long-Term Prognosis From a Large 
Prospective Study.

Gaita F(#)(1)(2), Cerrato N(#)(3), Giustetto C(#)(2)(4), Martino A(5), 
Bergamasco L(6), Millesimo M(2)(4), Barbonaglia L(7), Carvalho P(8), Caponi 
