PMCID: PMC10637308
PMID: 37830188 [Indexed for MEDLINE]

Conflict of interest statement: Disclosures None.


145. Am J Biol Anthropol. 2023 Oct 13. doi: 10.1002/ajpa.24861. Online ahead of 
